<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440227>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. a, Map of collection sites for the specimens in this study and other locations globally where the same species have been collected; b, view of the Central and Eastern Indo-Pacific region; c, new black coral records from the Coral Sea." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440227/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440235>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Parantipathes cf. hirondelle: a, G62019, side-view showing pinnule density along the stem; b, G35429, section of corallum showing pinnule orientation and density; c, G35429, cross-sectional view of the pinnules; d, G35429, spines on a section of pinnule." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440235/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440237>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Schizopthes affinis: a, G61837, anterolateral view of corallum showing pinnule density, triangular corallum shape, and curved hook at basal end b, G61978, spines on a pinnule shows bifucation of some polypar spines (seen on left side of image) and larger polypar spines than abpolypar spines; c, G61837, spine on a section of a pinnule." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440237/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

